{"tid":2212091,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"［自家烘焙］忌廉蛋糕卷","createTime":"2020-09-21T13:47:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-22T10:26:44.000Z","uid":132749,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"43cb043c8aeaa0e2e239c8fe63a36fe0dc36c563","tid":2212091,"uid":132749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T13:47:30.000Z","msg":"今次整左蛋糕卷，平時一般係街買到既係butter cream, 自己整改左用cream去整，濕潤好多， 加上味道香好多。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後一次係係x心買，用buttercream食落好乾，宜家仲黑心<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雪完一晚之後食，宜次用既海棉蛋糕做法水份比較多，又吸左忌廉入去， 凍冰冰， 勁好食。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果有d 芒果加落去仲好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可惜唔係時候，買唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n個日上網見介紹樂天有個拿破崙夾蛋糕卷，勁吸引，下次有時間時試下整<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JPajuU7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJPajuU7.jpg&h=699b5099&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m6HaBAa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm6HaBAa.jpg&h=21d79152&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/z5CFZpk1O84\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fz5CFZpk1O84&d=UI3sabJMorhQDzR%2BXF3zEbY5fiapVNQoBN5VkmpLYQk%3D&h=c1d6d2a9\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/z5CFZpk1O84</a>"},{"pid":"13102958d8035b2e0364b6145094b83f1553df1d","tid":2212091,"uid":132749,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"43cb043c8aeaa0e2e239c8fe63a36fe0dc36c563","tid":2212091,"uid":132749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"re